And they used a traitor to try and trick Nehemiah.

00:35:49.099 --> 00:35:51.099
They're coming to kill you.

00:35:51.099 --> 00:35:56.099
By night, we must go into the temple and close the doors.

00:35:56.099 --> 00:35:59.099
Shemaah, should a man like me run away?

00:35:59.099 --> 00:36:01.099
You don't understand.

00:36:01.099 --> 00:36:04.099
What would that do to the spirit of the entire nation?

00:36:04.099 --> 00:36:06.099
It's the only safe place.

00:36:06.099 --> 00:36:09.099
Besides, I'm not a priest.

00:36:09.099 --> 00:36:12.099
If I entered the temple, that would be valid reason to kill me.

00:36:12.099 --> 00:36:15.099
I will not go in.

00:36:15.099 --> 00:36:17.099
That decision would be foolish, Nehemiah.

00:36:17.099 --> 00:36:25.659
Oh, I see.

00:36:25.659 --> 00:36:30.659
Tobiah and San Ballet put you up to this dint they you hypocrite.

00:36:30.659 --> 00:36:32.659
Made you hover remember them?

00:36:32.659 --> 00:36:36.659
And all of you false prophets who keep trying to frighten me.

00:36:36.659 --> 00:36:37.659
Come here Nehemiah.

00:36:37.659 --> 00:36:44.039
We have work to do.

00:36:44.039 --> 00:36:47.039
Three schemes, three failures.

00:36:47.039 --> 00:36:50.039
So lesson number two.

00:36:50.039 --> 00:36:59.039
Like Nehemiah, we might encounter opposers who scheme to bring our loyal service to a halt.

00:36:59.039 --> 00:37:03.039
Some may invite us to meet them halfway, so to speak.

00:37:03.039 --> 00:37:09.039
They may try to convince us that if we served Jehovah with just a little less zeal,

00:37:09.039 --> 00:37:14.039
we could pursue worldly goals at the same time.

00:37:14.039 --> 00:37:18.039
However, because God's kingdom comes first in our lives,

00:37:18.039 --> 00:37:22.039
we can be like Nehemiah and refuse to compromise.

00:37:22.039 --> 00:37:25.039
We know where this world's hidden.

00:37:25.039 --> 00:37:30.929
Opposers also spread false accusations against us.

00:37:30.929 --> 00:37:34.929
In some lands, we're accused of posing a threat to the state.

00:37:34.929 --> 00:37:39.929
Some accusations have been successfully rebutted in court.

00:37:39.929 --> 00:37:47.929
But whatever the outcome, we're confident that Jehovah will direct matters according to his will.

00:37:47.929 --> 00:37:53.929
Opposition may also come from those who pretend to serve Jehovah.

00:37:53.929 --> 00:37:59.929
Just as a fellow Jew tried to get Nehemiah to break God's law to save his life,

00:37:59.929 --> 00:38:06.929
so former witnesses may try to get us to compromise in one way or another.

00:38:06.929 --> 00:38:12.929
However, we reject apostates because we know that our lives are saved,

00:38:12.929 --> 00:38:17.929
not by breaking God's laws, but by keeping them.

00:38:17.929 --> 00:38:23.929
Each time Nehemiah refused to fall into their trap, why?

00:38:23.929 --> 00:38:26.929
Because he had a brilliant mind? No.

00:38:26.929 --> 00:38:34.929
It was because he relied on Jehovah and Jehovah gave him the insight needed

00:38:34.929 --> 00:38:38.929
to see through their deceptions.

00:38:38.929 --> 00:38:42.929
After the walls built, Nehemiah left Jerusalem for a while.

00:38:42.929 --> 00:38:46.929
But what did he find on his return?

00:38:46.929 --> 00:38:53.929
Instead of coming back to find true worship thriving, he found it barely surviving.

00:38:53.929 --> 00:38:59.929
All the work that he had done to help the people to trust Jehovah.

00:38:59.929 --> 00:39:02.929
How do you think he felt?

00:39:02.929 --> 00:39:06.929
He could have said, that's it. I'm out.

00:39:06.929 --> 00:39:10.929
Let someone else clean this up and walk away.

00:39:10.929 --> 00:39:13.929
But did he? Let's watch again.

00:39:13.929 --> 00:39:17.929
Why have you and the deputy rulers neglected the House of God?

00:39:17.929 --> 00:39:20.929
You and they please cleanse this room.

00:39:20.929 --> 00:39:26.929
You know God's law, no work, no business on the Sabbath.

00:39:26.929 --> 00:39:27.929
Go!

00:39:27.929 --> 00:39:33.929
Did you not swear, never to marry someone who doesn't serve Jehovah?

00:39:33.929 --> 00:39:38.929
Then why have you ignored the command of Jehovah and your own oath?

